e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T06:43:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Posh</blockquote><br />\npush"},{"pid":"54b84d11b2367463ed6df60202e94ae849698a3f","tid":138950,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:52:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>過多十幾年 香港人嘅定義係咩</blockquote><br />\n唔駛十幾年，而家d小學生好似講蝗語既多過廣東話，仲要應該有d係真香港人為左大多數蝗蟲同學而主動講蝗語</blockquote><br />\n葵青好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去親m記一定聽到普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfae4ecb32dd15968d69e259699a7702617d02bb","tid":138950,"uid":442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:01:17.000Z","msg":"係大興球場行一個圈真係得一兩個人講廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b18be9258cabcda5d5dbf837741a4d114b8c6f08","tid":138950,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:03:29.000Z","msg":"死返上去啦"}]}